### 2. **csv-data-parser.php**
<augment_code_snippet path="csv-data-parser.php" mode="EXCERPT">
```php
function parseAndGenerateCSV($rawData, $fileType = null, $targetFolder) {
    $rawData = mb_convert_encoding($rawData, 'UTF-8', 'UTF-16LE');
    $cleanedCsvDir = __DIR__ . "/cleaned-csv/" . $targetFolder . "/";

    $records = array_filter(explode('$|', $rawData));
    $headerRow = [];
    if (!empty($records[0])) {
        $headerRow = array_map('trim', explode('|@|', preg_replace('/[\x00-\x1F\x80-\xFF]/', '', $records[0])));
    }
```
</augment_code_snippet>

**Purpose**: Utility function to parse raw pipe-delimited data and convert it to clean CSV format using PhpSpreadsheet. Handles encoding conversion and data cleaning.

